        "Name": "MercNews Broadcast",
        "Details": "[[DM.Factions[faction_Marian],MARIAN HEGEMONY]] ANNEXES [[DM.Factions[faction_Illyrian],Illyrian Palatinate]]!\r\n\n\nAlphard, [[DM.Factions[faction_Marian],Marian Hegemony]]: Two legions of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMHAF],Marian Hegemony Armed Forces]] defeated the mercenary armed forces of the [[DM.Factions[faction_Illyrian],Illyrian Palatinate]], crushing the Arms of Thor battalions outright, and fighting Cavanough’s Cavalry to a stalemate where the Cavalry ultimately surrendered to and joined the [[DM.Factions[faction_Marian],Marian Hegemony]] Armed Forces. The [[DM.Factions[faction_Illyrian],Illyrian Palatinate]] joins the [[DM.Factions[faction_Lothian],Lothian League]] as the most recent realms to fall in the Hegemony’s expansion campaign.\r\n\n\nWould you like to know more?",
